00:24:43.582 --> 00:24:45.085
may be well aware
of the fact that...

390
00:24:45.218 --> 00:24:47.420
Gonna make my way upstairs.

391
00:24:47.554 --> 00:24:48.755
Are made from some of

392
00:24:48.888 --> 00:24:50.457
