00:25:54.454 --> 00:25:55.614
Sold to the lady in the back.

410
00:25:55.722 --> 00:25:56.589
Thank you very much.

411
00:25:56.723 --> 00:25:58.825
The cross is up next, kid.

412
00:25:58.958 --> 00:26:00.226
Um...

