466
00:28:08.722 --> 00:28:11.090
Stupid door.

467
00:28:12.592 --> 00:28:15.295
Okay. Um...

468
00:28:15.428 --> 00:28:16.996
Oh, God.

469
00:28:17.130 --> 00:28:19.330
